data.description: The Delray is a 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage floor plan located on an oversized - largest in the community & backs up to privacy - cul-de-sac lot in The Preserve at Paradise Cove! This home features 9' ceilings, insulated interior walls, and EVP flooring throughout, including all bedrooms - no carpet! Kitchen and baths have upgraded quartz countertops. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances including a smooth top double oven range, over the range microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator. Washer and dryer are negotiable. Previous homeowners added ceiling fans in all bedrooms, custom window trim to all windows, wainscoting in foyer, and crown molding in primary bedroom and common areas. Beautiful white painted shaker style cabinetry in kitchen and baths. This home is ready for immediate occupancy. Call today for more information.
